    Import a dataset from monolix (based on an imported model)

    monolixDataImport(ui, data, na.strings = c("NA", "."))

    Arguments

    ui

    A rxode2 ui model imported from monolix

    data

    dataset to convert to nlmixr2 format; if the dataset is missing, load from the mlxtran specification

    na.strings

    a character vector of strings which are to be interpreted as NA values. Blank fields are also considered to be missing values in logical, integer, numeric and complex fields. Note that the test happens after white space is stripped from the input (if enabled), so na.strings values may need their own white space stripped in advance.

    Value

    Dataset appropriate for using with the rxode2 model for simulations
